I suddenly awoke.[p]
Where is this place? [p]
Why am I here? [p]
Was I brought here by someone? [p]
There is no boundary between dream and reality, just confusion.[p]
As I lay on the bench seat in the cafe my eyes slowly begin to focus.[p]
The woman sitting at the counter stands and folds her arms. [p]
She walks over and looks down at me.[p]


