She is wearing a police uniform.[p]
The woman smiles a little bit, as she appears to be relieved that I have regained consciousness.[p]
"It looks like you have come around."[p]
"Who are you?"[p]
I try talking to the unfamiliar woman.[p]
"I'm Cybil.[p]
Cybil Bennet.[p]
I'm here because all communication with this town suddenly went dead and so I came to investigate."[p]
"I'm...Harry Mason. I brought my daughter to this town for some sightseeing, [p]
but on the way there was an accident and I lost consciousness...[p]
Oh, yeah, Cybil...You haven't seen a little girl in this town have you?"[p]


